                            readability improvements).</entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/customizing_ai_positron_for_your_dita_xml_project.dita" xtrc="entry:4;39:32" colname="col2" dita-ot:x="2" dita-ot:y="2">The company specific style guide might impose certain rules that, by
