            <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/customizing_ai_positron_for_your_dita_xml_project.dita" xtrc="title:8;262:20">Conclusion</title>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/customizing_ai_positron_for_your_dita_xml_project.dita" xtrc="p:26;263:16">You need to invest time to adapt the AI Positron add-on to generate better content
